Despite the significant findings that lobster length in 2017 was larger 2012 for Isla Vista, an MPA site, there is a small effect size and number of observations was very low for 2012 (6 observations). On the other hand, lobsters at Mohawk Reef (a non-MPA site) were significantly smaller in 2017 than in 2012, with a medium effect size. (NOTE TO SELF:NEEDS TO BE RE-WORDED)
